==============================================================================

n₁ ~ 3p²/π² (Farey size), so n₁/(p-1) ~ 3p/π²
This grows linearly in p, while Σ₁ and δΣ grow logarithmically.
So for large enough p, n₁·δΣ >> (p-1)·Σ₁ automatically!

